{
  "texts": [
    "Highlighted in Table 1, the benchmarks reveal that, particularly in tasks such as property prediction, GPT-4 outperforms traditional machine learning models like random forest and XGBoost in accuracy across multiple datasets.",
    "Similarly, GPT-4 stands out in yield prediction and reagents selection tasks, demonstrating superior performance indicative of its advanced reasoning capabilities in classification-based chemical problems.",
    "ScienceQA (Lu et al., 2022) is a benchmark for natural science domain question answering with 21,208 multimodal multiple-choice science questions derived from textbooks.",
    "It divides natural science topics such as biology, chemistry, and physics into categories that include solutions; physical and chemical changes; atoms and molecules; and chemical reactions.",
    "The tasks include multiple-choice questions, short-answer questions, and explanation questions."
  ]
}